00:10:32.240 --> 00:10:32.960
Beautiful.

00:10:32.960 --> 00:10:34.639
Any questions?

00:10:34.639 --> 00:10:35.759
Just one.

00:10:35.759 --> 00:10:37.279
Every week, I have meetings.

00:10:37.279 --> 00:10:39.159
Excuse me.

00:10:39.159 --> 00:10:39.919
Yes?

00:10:39.919 --> 00:10:41.360
Gene Weber is online, too.

00:10:41.360 --> 00:10:43.200
Thank you.

00:10:43.200 --> 00:10:44.639
Listen, I got to take this.

00:10:44.639 --> 00:10:46.840
Did you want to tell me something?

00:10:46.840 --> 00:10:47.759
No, nothing.

00:10:47.759 --> 00:10:49.039
It can wait.

00:10:49.039 --> 00:10:50.200
Very good.

00:10:50.200 --> 00:10:53.080
Al, why don't you take David, show him around,

00:10:53.080 --> 00:10:55.480
and then take him down to HR to make it official.

00:10:55.480 --> 00:10:57.799
David Barker, welcome to True North.

00:10:57.799 --> 00:11:02.740
Thank you, Mr. Benson.

00:11:02.740 --> 00:11:07.620
My friend, let me introduce you to a new home away from home.

00:11:07.620 --> 00:11:09.019
I give you the lay of the lands.

